    ogg-vorbis ( libogg, libvorbis, vorbis-tools )

        a completely open, patent-free audio encoding and streaming technology

            libogg

                ./configure --prefix=/opt/ogg-vorbis && make
                sudo make install

            libvorbis

                ./configure --prefix=/opt/ogg-vorbis && make
                sudo make install

            sudo ln -s /opt/ogg-vorbis/include/ogg /usr/include/ogg
            sudo ln -s /opt/ogg-vorbis/include/vorbis /usr/include/vorbis

            vorbis-tools

                ./configure --prefix=/opt/ogg-vorbis && make
                sudo make install

